Class DelegatingAdapterFactory<T>

java.lang.Object
org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.impl.AdapterFactoryImpl
org.nasdanika.emf.ComposeableAdapterFactoryImpl
org.nasdanika.emf.DelegatingAdapterFactory<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.AdapterFactory, ComposeableAdapterFactory
Direct Known Subclasses:
BiFunctionAdapterFactory, FunctionAdapterFactory, InstanceAdapterFactory, SupplierAdapterFactory
public abstract class DelegatingAdapterFactory<T> extends ComposeableAdapterFactoryImpl
Base class for adapter factories delegating to Supplier or FunctionFactory to create an adapter and wrapping adapter into a dynamic proxy if the adapter does not implement Adapter.
Author:
Pavel Vlasov
